<p class="">The hon. Gentleman has got this wrong. He keeps on talking about the Persians paying us £25 million for the Abadan Refinery. I have explained how the figure was arrived at. It is not a payment for the Abadan refinery because, indeed, the consortium of operating companies engaged in the refining of oil will be operating the refinery.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
