            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-942a0595-d748-4d8a-abe9-6d1647755bc7">
                Mr. Thomas Reid  (Swindon)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-942a0595-d748-4d8a-abe9-6d1647755bc7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
