            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c8050471-2998-4cc0-8c9c-c983efbf73b4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
