<p class="">Forty per cent.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-36fa3e5a-6103-425d-ae6c-4cdc8dbf06f4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
